name: Server Call Counter (E1)
description: Counts every Server Call (Event plus Pageview Hits)

name: Page View Counter (E2)
description: Counts every Pageview Hit

name: Checkout Step: Payment (E3)
description: Counts when user reaches the Payment Step in the Checkout

name: Checkout Step: Overview (E4)
description: Counts when user reaches the Order Overview Step in the Checkout (final step before order confirmation)

name: Fast Checkout (E6)
description: Counts Hits when a user is in a fast checkout

name: Order Commission (E7)
description: Commission of the Order

name: Product Commission (E8)
description: Commission per Purchase per Product

name: Repeat Orders (E9)
description: Counts on a purchase if a user has bought already in the past (determined by a cookie)

name: Order Tax (E10)
description: The overall tax sum of a purchase

name: Order Shipping (E11)
description: The overall shipping sum of a purchase

name: Product Revenue with Discount (E12)
description: The revenue made with vouchers on product level

name: Order Voucher Discount (E13)
description: Voucher Tracking: Discount in CHF of Order

name: Product Voucher Discount (E14)
description: Voucher Tracking: Discount in CHF of Product (Tax without vouchers)

name: Order Discounted Tax (E15)
description: The overall discounted tax sum of a purchase

name: Int. Stand. Search Result Clicked (E16)
description: Counts the clicks on internal standard search results (not suggested search)

name: Active Stand. Search Started (E17)
description: Counts every time the internal (not suggested) search is started by clicking on the Search button

name: Sugg. Search Result Clicked (E18)
description: Counts every time an internal suggested search result is clicked.

name: Stand. Search started from Sugg. Search (E19)
description: Counts when the standard search is started even though the user saw search result previews in the suggested search (user clicked "show all" or the search button)

name: Registration (any form) (E20)
description: Counts any Registration attempt no matter where (checkout or account)

name: Sugg. Search Category Lvl3 Clicked (E21)
description: Counts clicks on Category Level3 Suggestions

name: Successful Active Stand. Search (E22)
description: Counts a successful Active Standard Search (when the user clicks on a result for a search term he previously searched actively or reaches a PDP with the search term in the referrer string)

name: Hit of Logged in User (E23)
description: Counts every HIt by logged-in users

name: Hit of Registered User (E24) - notyet active
description: Counts every HIt by a user that has registered in the past (had a user cookie in the past)

name: Newsletter Subscriber (E27)
description: Counts whether someone is a NL Subscriber (enriched via Audience Stream)

name: AudienceStream Returning Visitor (E28)
description: Counts if the Visitor has been to the site before according to Audience Stream Visitor Stitching

name: Hit with third-party cookies disabled (E29)
description: Hit with third-party cookies disabled according to AudienceStream

name: Internal User (E30)
description: Identifies an internal user (Siroop)

name: Offline Ad Cost (E31)
description: Offline Cost (e.g. TV)

name: Offline GRP (E32)
description: GRP (Gross Rating Point = Reach within target audience) of offline campaigns

name: Impressions (E35)
description: Ad Impressions per Campaign ID according to Ad Serving Network

name: Clicks (E36)
description: Ad Clicks per Campaign ID according to Ad Serving Network

name: Ad Cost (E37)
description: Cost per day per Campaign ID according to Ad Serving Network

name: View-through Conversions (E38)
description: View-Through Conversions per Campaign ID according to Ad Serving Network

name: Refunded Revenue (E41)
description: The revenue (CHF) that was refunded

name: Refunded Orders (E42)
description: The number of refunded orders

name: Refunded Units (E43)
description: The units (Stueckzahl) that were refunded

name: Cancelled Revenue (E44)
description: INACTIVE: The revenue (CHF) that was cancelled

name: Cancelled Orders (E45)
description: INACTIVE: The number of cancelled orders

name: Cancelled Units (E46)
description: INACTIVE: The units (Stueckzahl) that were cancelled

name: Hit with AudienceStream DLE (E47)
description: INACTIVE: Effective Revenue as recorded by the BI Team.  Delayed in reporting by about a week

name: Unique Lvl1 Categories (E48)
description: Number of Unique Lvl1 Categories in a basket. Allows to track mixed baskets where a user orders products from several Categories

name: Unique Lvl2 Categories (E49)
description: Number of Unique Lvl2 Categories in a basket. Allows to track mixed baskets where a user orders products from several Categories

name: Unique Lvl1-3 Categories (E50)
description: Number of Unique Lvl1-3 Categories in a basket. Allows to track mixed baskets where a user orders products from several Categories

name: Unique Products (for non-Prod Dimensions, deprecated) (E51)
description: Number of Unique Product Concrete IDs bought. Use for Dimensions like Campaigns. Deprecated since May 9, 2017. Recommended using E52.

name: Unique Products (E52)
description: Number of Unique Product Concrete IDs bought. Can be used for Product Dimensions or others. Available since May 9, 2017.

name: Unique Merchants (E53)
description: Number of Unique Merchants in a basket. Allows to track mixed baskets where a user orders products from several merchants

name: Active Merchant SKUs (E54)
description: Number of Products of a Merchant that are in stock (have an amount > 0)

name: Merchant SKUs (E55)
description: Number of Products of a Merchant indepedent of stock status

name: Concrete Prod Detail View (E56) - once per Pageview
description: zählt einmal pro Seitenaufruf den Concrete PDP View für eine Concrete ID

name: Abstract Prod Detail View (E57) - once per Page
description: zählt einmal pro Seitenaufruf den Abstract PDP View - bei Aufrufen von bereits konfigurierten Produkten wird auch gezählt. Kriterium: eec_action = "detail" AND has not been set yet on this page (ein Counter wird beim ersten Mal Zählen auf 1 gesetzt)

name: Merchant ProdPDV (E58) - once per Page, ID & Merchant
description:
Hits mit Concrete ID, zählt einmal pro Seitenaufruf.
Anwendungsfall: Uninflated Views eines Concrete Products (zB pro Merchant)
Kriterium: eec_action = "detail" AND prod_cid exists AND E58 has not been set yet on this page for this merchant & cid combo

name: Concrete Prod Detail View (E59)
description: zählt alle Hits mit Concrete ID - Anwendungsfall zB: Wie oft wird eine einzelne PDP konfiguriert, bevor das Produkt in den Warenkorb gelegt wird.

name: Abstract or Concrete Product Detail View (E60)
description:
zählt PDP Hits (analog zu GA, aber nicht mehrfach pro Merchant). Macht nur Sinn in once-per-Visit-Calc-Metriken
Kriterium: alle Hits mit eec_action = "detail"

name: Product View in List (E61)
description: Counts Product Views in Lists (available since Mid-April 2016, deactivated in June 2016)

name: Product List Click (E62) - since Jul 5/2017
description: Counts Clicks on Products in Lists (available since July 2017.)

name: Search Filter Load (E63)
description: User loaded a page where one or more filters were open

name: Login Success (E72)
description: Counts successful logins (tracked on the page after the logout)

name: Logout Success (E73)
description: Counts successful logouts (tracked on the page after the logout)

name: Login Fail (E74)
description: Counts failed login attempts

name: Registration Fail (E75)
description: Counts failed Registration Attempts (e.g. because user email already exists)

name: PDP Video View (E77)
description: Product Video View on PDP

name: PDP Image Click (E78)
description: Product Image Click on PDP

name: Wishlist View (E80)
description: User views wishlist page

name: Wishlist Add (E81)
description: User adds product to wishlist

name: Wishlist Remove (E82)
description: User removes product from wishlist

name: Cart Add from Wishlist (E83)
description: User adds product from wishlist to cart

name: Page Load Time: Response from Server (E85)
description: Time from "request is sent" to "last byte of response has been received"

name: Page Load Time: DOM Ready (E86)
description: Time from "browser is ready to fetch document" to "document has loaded"

name: Page Load Time: Load Complete (E87)
description: Time from "browser is ready to fetch document" to "page with all resources has loaded"

name: Test Counter Event (E97)
description: Test Event for Counter Values

name: Test Numeric Event (E98)
description: Test Event for Numeric Values

name: Test Currency Event (E99)
description: Test Event for Currency Values

name: Data Source Import Event (E100)
description: Is set whenever a Full Processing Data Source Import is made. Used to easily filter out these Hits

name: DFA Clicks (E901)
description: Tracks the number of times users clicked a specific DFA banner ad. (Automatically populated through a data feed by DFA Data Connector integration, event name cannot be altered.)

name: DFA Impressions (E902)
description: Tracks the number of time a specific DFA ad was served.. (Automatically populated through a data feed by DFA Data Connector integration, event name cannot be altered.)

name: DFA Media Cost (E903)
description: Contains the media cost metrics that have been input in the DFA interface.
